  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 10 \u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0d85\u0d9b\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dc0 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf - \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0da0\u0dca\u0da1\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd6\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel will continue from July 10 - President ready for talks with Russia",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Minister Mahindananda Aluthgamage said that a program has been prepared to provide fuel continuously from July 10. He stated this at a media briefing held in Colombo today.",
        "He said that funds have already been allocated for the importation of medicines for the coming year and that arrangements have already been made to supply the required gas for the next three months from July 5.",
        "\"The President has already talked to the Russian President over the phone and sent a letter to the Russian President through the embassy to reach an agreement. The necessary arrangements are being discussed with Russia.",
        "The President also hopes to visit the United Arab Emirates in the near future to obtain fuel. The government has so far provided positive solutions to some of the serious problems faced by the people. \u201d"
      ],
